                                            </div>
                                            <div class="st__item st-header__item st-header__item--active st-header__item--sortable" style="--st-base-width: 5.5rem;">
                                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon">
